Package ca.ualbert.cs.tasko.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectivityReceiver
    Receives Broadcasts for CONNECTIVITY_STATE and will set ConnectivityState and execute any pending commands if there are any from the offline state.
    ConnectivityState
    Simple wrapper class to keep track of connectivity issues.
    DataCommandManager
    DataCommandManager is a commandManager for the dataCommands.
    DataManager
    The DataManager class is built to provide an abstraction to elastic search functionality.
    JestWrapper
    Provides a few simple methods to work with the Jest Client
    LocalDataManager
    LocalDataManager provides an abstraction and various useful methods to manage Local Data and pending offline Data Commands.
    MockDataManager
    MockDataManager class that serves as a mock DataManager class and returns fake information to the test classes for testing purposes
    RuntimeTypeAdapterFactory<T>
    Adapts values whose runtime type may differ from their declaration type.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoInternetException
    This exception is thrown when the methods that depend on internet are called when there is no internet.
